Sample_title: ATAC-seq in MSCs infected with EWSFLI1 (rep3)
Sample_extract_protocol_ch1: 5x10^4 cells for each condition were first incubated in hypotonic buffer then resuspended in lysis buffer, centrifugated and resuspended in Transposase reaction mix for additional 30 min at 37C, following manufacturer recommendations (Nextera DNA sample Prep Kit, Illumina)., DNA was purified and adaptor sequences were added to the fragmented DNA by PCR to construct Illumina sequencing libraries. Purified PCR products were sequenced using the Illumina Nextseq device.
Sample_data_processing: Reads were aligned to hg19 using bwa. Reads that aligned in the proper orientation and on the same chromosome were then filtered to exclude PCR duplicates. Signal densities were calculated over a sliding 150 bp window at 20 bp steps and normalized to 10M reads in each experiment
sample_name: ATAC-seq in MSCs infected with EWSFLI1 (rep3)
